name: 1nC
description: This is an image still captured from a video art piece. If purchased, collector will receive a NFT in addition to the video file. The NFT is on the Tezos blockchain, which is known as a clean "cleanNFT", as it has less of an environment impact than some of the other cryptocurrencies currently available.  1nC is one of seven channels of video included in LIKES CHARGE, LIGHT TEAR, an exhibition at Nasher Sculpture Center in April 2021.
